  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate MK0476 and Fluticasone to Control Asthma in Patients With Mild Persistent Asthma (0476-910)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Double-Dummy, Multicenter Study to Evaluate and Compare Oral Montelukast and Inhaled Fluticasone in the Control of Asthma for 6- to 14-Year-Olds With Mild Persistent Asthma</official_title>
